* CGS System of Unit Table
- Abbreviation: CGS or centimetre, gram, second.
|--------------------------------------+-------------------+--------|
| Quantity                             | Unit              | Symbol |
|--------------------------------------+-------------------+--------|
| distance (d), length (l), height (h) | centimetre        | cm     |
| mass (m)                             | gram              | g      |
| time (t)                             | second            | s      |
| speed (/v/), velocity (v)              | centimetre/second | cm/s   |
| acceleration (a)                     | gal               | Gal    |
| force (F)                            | dyne              | dyn    |
| pressure (P or p)                    | barye             | Ba     |
| energy (E, Q, W)                     | erg               | erg    |
| power (P)                            | erg/s             | erg/s  |
| viscosity (Î¼)                        | poise             | P      |
|--------------------------------------+-------------------+--------|
